Hailing from Detroit with his first release, Secoya is going to make you Run for the nearest Hospital with his heavy dancefloor stompers that are already gaining support from the scene's World Champs. On the menu, glitch, dubstep, d&b, insane vocals and a distinct signature sound as well as fat remixes. Although he's still young in the scene, Secoya has shown us he's ready to level Up and take things to the next dimension.....
